		<div class="pd_name"> Social Sightseeing: The 21st century way of travelling</div>
		<br/>
		Do you hate being shepherded through boring museums and churches on an organized tour? Do you hate the smoothly oiled machinery of modern mass tourism that never lets you look behind the pretty facade of your destination? Are you tired of the countless scams you encounter in tourist destinations because you weren't aware of the local pitfalls? 
		<br/><br/>
		Then we have something for you: Social Sightseeing, the 21st century way of travelling. Don't be a lost sheep abroad anymore when you travel! Watch our 1 minute video - and you'll know everything you need!

